      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLAZING EARLY (5) has an impressive record and comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at Rockhampton, scoring by one length (23.47). Brilliant beginner who should be leading the way here. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Form reads well for this. WAIKARIE KATIE (1) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.20 beating Cyclone Saskia. Won at her only start from this box. Expected to feature again. MONTY ZOOMER (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (22.37) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. STORMY MUSTANG (2) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.",
